ğŸš€ Portfolio Application with Authentication
A modern, full-stack portfolio application built using Flask and React. It features user authentication, profile management, and dynamic content updates with a responsive and clean UI.

ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack
ğŸ”§ Backend
Technology	Description
Flask	Lightweight Python web framework
SQLite	Lightweight, file-based database
SQLAlchemy	ORM for managing database models
Flask-Login	User session and authentication management
Flask-WTF	Secure form handling and validation
Flask-Mail	Email integration for password reset
Werkzeug	Password hashing and security utilities
Python-dotenv	Environment variable configuration

ğŸ¨ Frontend
Technology	Description
React 18	Declarative UI library
TypeScript	Strongly typed JavaScript
Tailwind CSS	Utility-first CSS framework
Vite	Fast frontend build tool
Lucide React	Icon library for elegant UI components

